# Assets Directory

This directory is reserved for PNG background images exported from Visily.

## Expected Asset Files:

- `landing-hero.png` - Landing page hero background (1920×800px recommended)
- `persona-hero.png` - Persona page hero background (1920×600px recommended) 
- `dashboard-hero.png` - Dashboard header background (1920×400px recommended)
- `community-hero.png` - Community header background (1920×500px recommended)
- `profile-hero.png` - Profile header background (1920×400px recommended)

## Usage:

Assets will be referenced in components using standard public path:
```jsx
<div 
  className="hero-section"
  style={{ backgroundImage: 'url(/assets/landing-hero.png)' }}
>
